novations to Canadian garden enthusiasts. This season marks the launch of SUNBITE F1, an innovative baby potato variety that combines late-blight resistance with the convenience of seed planting. Through Hortinova’s established distribution network — from retail garden centers to online platforms —  SUNBITE F1 makes it simple for Canadian gardeners to grow healthy, vigorous, and disease-resistant potatoes directly from hybrid true potato seeds.<br\/><br\/><br\/><br\/><\/p>","text_size":"large"}},"button_4UPAdd":{"type":"button","settings":{"button_label":"Discover SUNBITE F1","link":"shopify:\/\/products\/sunbite-f1-hybrid-true-potato-seed-gardening-farming","button_size":"large","button_style":"solid"}}},"block_order":["title_YNMmUk","text_HR3KqE","button_4UPAdd"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.name","settings":{"height":"small","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Solynta_Seeds.jpg","image_position":"top","image_crop":true,"text_alignment":"horizontal-left","is_fullwidth":false,"remove_margin":false,"color_background_main":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","color_text_main":"#19212c","color_borders_main":"#ffffff","color_hide_borders":false}},"1655112847aaa4cc50":{"type":"newsletter","settings":{"show_icon":true,"title":"STAY AHEAD WITH HORTINOVA","text":"<p>JOIN OUR NEWSLETTER FOR UPDATES ON NEW VARIETIES, CULTIVATION INSIGHTS, AND EXCLUSIVE OFFERS TAILORED FOR GROWERS OF ALL KINDS — FROM HOME ENTHUSIASTS TO PROFESSIONALS.<br\/><br\/><\/p>","color_background_main":"#008080","color_text_main":"#ffffff","color_borders_main":"rgba(0,0,0,0)"}}},"order":["1653646142d6a7c886","cb8efefa-1297-47f9-8b0c-75398a18ba13","e6855973-ce86-4731-8139-ebe857087a38","165407625224b5d2af","496cdfb9-a6e6-46a9-b455-691ca3a994c6","1654161920efe5f084","16551074833cdf378e","d068c685-9c8e-49f2-b547-001d48503ce0","08293d8d-e88f-40c7-ac11-ec79a4b28353","ef78cdb1-04d7-4236-836d-c9c58e7c631d","featured-collection","16546982542e923b5a","16551212489c663a1e","1ea0a65c-437d-4835-adc4-5c64bfdaf973","4dcfbe0b-1942-449d-800